# custom.txt.example — copy this file to custom.txt to get started:
#   cp allowlist-cidrs.d/custom.txt.example allowlist-cidrs.d/custom.txt
#
# custom.txt is gitignored so your internal IPs stay out of version control.
# Always included regardless of which components are enabled.
# Add explicit proxy IPs or narrow CIDRs here when agent traffic routes through
# a corporate proxy. Do not use broad catch-all ranges (0.0.0.0/0, ::/0).
#
# Examples:
#   10.20.30.40/32    # corporate proxy
#   2001:db8::/48     # corporate IPv6 range
